{"id": 5235, "title": "Ticket #5235: Apply VanillaToGrid transforms after job hook", "description": "<blockquote>\nVanillaToGrid::vanillaToGrid applies a bunch of transforms that are needed for any routed job.\n\n<p>These don't appear to get called after a hook - but it's not apparent why.  It only does really simple transforms (think \"remove <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=BufferSize\" title=\"Buffer Size\">BufferSize</a></span> attribute\") that even hook users will want (but not want the tedium of copy/pasting from HTCondor source code).\n\n</p><p>Might as well move these into <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=FinishSubmitJob\" title=\"Finish Submit Job\">FinishSubmitJob</a></span> to be executed from the hook.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Nov-23 12:46</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=49639\">[49639]</a></span>: Docs for Job Router standard transforms when using TRANSLATE_JOB hook. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5235\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5235'); return false;\" title=\"Apply VanillaToGrid transforms after job hook\">#5235</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Oct-14 10:42</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=49434\">[49434]</a></span>: Make gridresource optional in vanillaToGrid(). <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5235\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5235'); return false;\" title=\"Apply VanillaToGrid transforms after job hook\">#5235</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Aug-26 15:53</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45701\">[45701]</a></span>: Apply <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=VanillaToGrid\" title=\"Vanilla To Grid\">VanillaToGrid</a></span> to all routed jobs. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5235\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5235'); return false;\" title=\"Apply VanillaToGrid transforms after job hook\">#5235</a></span>  (By Brian Bockelman )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2016-Nov-23 12:47", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-Aug-25 22:43", "fixed_version": "2015-Aug-25 22:43", "broken_version": "", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "DaemonsSubmitNode", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "bbockelm", "rust": "", "customer_group": "osg", "visibility": "public", "notify": "bbockelm@cse.unl.edu", "due_date": ""}